# Plan functions

Plans can use functions that are built into Bolt and Puppet. This reference
page includes a list of built-in Bolt functions. To see a list of built-in
Puppet functions, see Puppet's [built-in function
reference](https://puppet.com/docs/puppet/latest/function.html).

<% for func in @functions %>
## `<%= func['name'] %>`

<%= func['desc'] %>

<% func['signatures'].each_with_index do |sig, i| -%>
<% unless func['signatures'].count == 1 -%>
**Signature <%= i + 1 %>**

<%= sig['desc'] %>
<% end -%>

```
<%= sig['signature'] %>
```

