an object with the type <%= sig['return'] %> and accepts the following
parameter<%= sig['params'].count == 1 ? '' : 's' %>:

| Parameter | Type | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
<% sig['params'].each do |name, data| -%>
| `<%= name %>` | <%= data['type'] %> | <%= data['desc'] %> |
<% end %>

